{
  "texts": [
    "It is a stochastic generating process.",
    "It means that even for the same input, the actual encoding will vary slightly on each run owing to sampling even while the mean and standard deviation will remain the same [98].The goal of the autoencoder is to minimize both its latent loss and reconstruction loss, which measures how closely the autoencoder's output resembles its input.",
    "(how close its hidden nodes were to a normal distribution).",
    "Less information can be encoded with a smaller latent loss, which increases the reconstruction loss.",
    "As a result, the latent loss and the reconstruction loss must be traded off by the VAE."
  ]
}